-- Leighton Monitoring ACS Takeover Proposal of Construction Company Hochtief
-- B y   J a s o n   S c o t t
-- 2010-10-05T07:19:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/leighton-urges-shareholders-to-stand-still-on-acs-bid-for-parent-hochtief.html
Leighton Holdings Ltd. urged
shareholders to take no action in relation to their Leighton
shares after Actividades de Construccion & Servicios SA made a
takeover bid for its majority shareholder, Germany’s Hochtief
AG. Leighton said in a statement to the Australian stock
exchange today that it treats matters regarding its minority
shareholders “extremely seriously.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
